title: *PATREON PREVIEW* The Biggest Belle at the Ball
description:
Jimmy, Larry and Chef podding in person for the first time since March? Yeah, you’re probably gonna wanna change your headphones because shit is wet. The Big Three—Chuck’s words—are hanging out, getting absolutely smashed and discussing a variety of topics including, but not limited to: battling to become the apple of Jonah Hill’s eye, Supreme flipping itself for $2.1 billion, respectfully celebrating Trump’s L, teasing Throwing Fits’ next product release and much more.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
